rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0001
rows.name: Tell me you got it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0002
rows.name: Yes, sir.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0003
rows.name: Thank God. Let's get it analyzed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0004
rows.name: Commander, hold on.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0005
rows.name:
Lao's still back at the Ganglion base in Cauldros.
He's seriously injured.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0006
rows.name:
Yeah? ...And?
What exactly are you getting at?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0007
rows.name:
I know you aren't suggesting we help
that back-stabbing bastard? He tried to kill you guys![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0008
rows.name: I am, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0009
rows.name:
He's been through a lot, Commander.
You know his story as well as anyone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0010
rows.name: [ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0011
rows.name: When we signed off on Project Exodus,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0012
rows.name:
we knew there'd be cases like Lao.
Potentially hundreds of them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0013
rows.name:
Look at Irina.
She's still struggling with losing her brother.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0014
rows.name:
But we moved forward anyway,
for the greater good of mankind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0015
rows.name: Irina didn't try to kill us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0016
rows.name:
In fact, she's been doing everything she can
to help further BLADE's cause.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0017
rows.name: Are you sure?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0018
rows.name: Hmm?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0019
rows.name: According to Gwin,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0020
rows.name: she's been acting strange, reckless...almost suicidal...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0021
rows.name: He thinks maybe she wants to die...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0023
rows.name:
It takes different forms,
but it's coming from the same place as Lao.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0024
rows.name:
Of course, it's no excuse for what he's doneâ€”
just putting it in perspective.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0025
rows.name: Fine. We'll bring him in.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0026
rows.name: Oh, thank you. Thank you so much, Commander![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0027
rows.name:
I wouldn't get too excited about it...
Especially after I break every bone in his body...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs11110100_MSG0028
rows.name:
It's going to take a bit to complete the analysis.
Let's regroup at the barracks.[ST:wait ]
